eaves-key-lending-benchmarks-unchanged-expected-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>央视称前中国足球高管因受贿被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-football-association-director-handed-7-years-jail-bribery-cctv-2024-08-20/</link><description>据中央电视台周二报道，中国足协原竞赛部主任黄松​​因受贿罪被判处有期徒刑七年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 01:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-football-association-director-handed-7-years-jail-bribery-cctv-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业宣布离岸债务重组协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-property-developer-kaisa-announces-offshore-debt-restructuring-agreement-2024-08-20/</link><description>中国佳兆业集团周二宣布与一批债权人达成境外债务重组协议，发行美元高级债券和强制性可转换债券。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:44:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-property-developer-kaisa-announces-offshore-debt-restructuring-agreement-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国谴责中国对菲律宾船只的“危险行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-dangerous-actions-by-china-against-philippine-vessels-2024-08-19/</link><description>美国国务院谴责中国周一在南海针对菲律宾船只的“危险行为”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:57:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-condemns-dangerous-actions-by-china-against-philippine-vessels-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场活跃，但中国利率下调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-19/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 21:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，普遍预计中国8月份将维持贷款基准LPR不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widely-expected-keep-lending-benchmark-lprs-unchanged-aug-2024-08-19/</link><description>路透社的一项调查显示，中国政策制定者在 7 月份下调了一系列关键利率，令全球市场感到意外，预计中国周二将维持基准贷款利率不变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 19:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widely-expected-keep-lending-benchmark-lprs-unchanged-aug-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>资金撤退，实物买家赢得铜市争夺战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</link><description>逃离铜市场的投资者可能会在数月内处于观望状态，这为预计主要消费国中国和其他地区的需求在未来几个月内恶化并对价格造成压力的实体参与者留下了空间。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/physical-buyers-win-battle-copper-market-funds-retreat-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：杰克逊霍尔迫在眉睫，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 10:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯猪肉生产商瞄准欧盟在中国猪肉市场的份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russian-pork-producers-target-eus-share-chinas-pork-market-2024-08-19/</link><description>俄罗斯猪肉生产商的目标是在未来几年内占据中国猪肉进口市场10%的份额，寻求利用欧盟与全球最大猪肉消费国中国之间的贸易紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russian-pork-producers-target-eus-share-chinas-pork-market-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>德国军舰等待穿越台湾海峡的命令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/german-warships-await-orders-crossing-disputed-taiwan-strait-2024-08-19/</link><description>两艘德国军舰的指挥官表示，两艘德国军舰正在等待柏林的命令，以确定下个月它们是否将成为数十年来第一批穿过台湾海峡的德国海军舰艇，此举遭到了北京的谴责。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/german-warships-await-orders-crossing-disputed-taiwan-strait-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>奥运选手在网上辱骂后，中国针对“混乱”的粉丝群体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-takes-aim-chaotic-fan-groups-after-olympians-abused-online-2024-08-19/</link><description>中国政府和官方体育机构谴责球迷利用社交媒体攻击和散布有关中国奥运选手的谣言，并表示这种行为对运动员、教练及其家人造成了极其负面的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 05:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-takes-aim-chaotic-fan-groups-after-olympians-abused-online-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>领导人会晤后，中国和越南签署了从铁路到鳄鱼的14项协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnams-top-leaders-meet-beijing-2024-08-19/</link><description>周一，中国国家主席习近平在北京会见越南新任领导人苏林后，中国和越南签署了涵盖跨境铁路和鳄鱼出口等领域的 14 份文件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 03:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vietnams-top-leaders-meet-beijing-2024-08-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>